<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recuperar Contraseña | SUPER ETENDART</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/main.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .box {
            background: #0d0d0d;
            border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #ffb703;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        p {
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #141414;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            background: #ffb703;
            color: #000;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="box">
        <h2>Recuperar Clave</h2>
        <p>Ingresá tu mail y te enviaremos un link para cambiar tu contraseña sin necesidad de poner la vieja.</p>

        <!-- 🔴 Cartel de Error si el correo no existe -->
        <% if (locals.error) { %>
            <div class="alerta-error"
                style="color: #ff4a4a; background: #2a1515; padding: 12px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 1px solid #ff0000; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
                ⚠️ <%= error %>
            </div>
            <% } %>

        <form action="/forgot" method="POST">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Tu Correo Electrónico" required>
            <button type="submit">Enviar Link de Recuperación</button>
        </form>
        <p style="margin-top:20px;"><a href="/login"
                style="color: #ffb703; text-decoration:none; font-size:14px;">Volver al Login</a></p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>